345
00:26:10,948 --> 00:26:12,698
but not all of us have that luxury.

346
00:26:12,699 --> 00:26:16,286
Which is what I find so
frustrating about you, Claire.

347
00:26:16,287 --> 00:26:18,788
You... you had a choice.

348
00:26:18,789 --> 00:26:20,664
